<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Weil</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass Konrad Zirkendorfer vielfach Nürnberger geschädigt hat, gewährt ihm aber bis Pfingsten vier Tage Geleit, um ihn anzuhören.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_96" id="47r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_96_r1l15">Der Stat cʒu wyle </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_96_r1l16"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Als vns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>freuntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von des ~ cʒirkendorffers </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_96_r1l17">handell wegen . das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> Nu tun vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_96_r1l18"> <expan>erſ<ex>amkeit</ex></expan> cʒuvviſſen . daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">vns </del> <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>cʒirkend<ex>orffer</ex></expan> vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> da <expan>ob<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_96_r1l19">vnd hiernẏden bederſeit groſʒ ſcheden getan hat . doch vvie darumb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_96_r1l20">So <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir das v̈mb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> in gutikeit ſteen laſſen hie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_96_r1l21"><expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd pfingſten ſchierſt komende Alſo . daʒ Er in <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_96_r1l22">cʒeite her cʒu vns kume So <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir Jm hie in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Stat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_96_r1l23">vier tag ein ſleht geleyte <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vor <expan>Allermen<ex>i</ex>kl<ex>ich</ex></expan> . vnd auſſerhalb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_96_r1l24">der Stat für vns vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ongeu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> vnd wollen ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_96_r1l25">rede gern darümb verhören . vnd wil Er das alſo <expan>aufneme<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_96_r1l26">ſo laſʒt vns des ewr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wıder vviſſen daʒ vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_96_r1l27">vns darnach vviſſen cʒu richten . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> valentini </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_96" id="47r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Wyle </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als uns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>freunts<ex>chaft</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von des Czirkendorffers
                        handell wegen, das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>. Nu tun wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ers<ex>amkeit</ex></expan> czu wissen, daz
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>Czirkend<ex>orffer</ex></expan> uns und den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> da <expan>ob<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                        hiernyden bederseit grosz scheden getan hat. Doch wie darumb so
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir das ümb
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> in gutikeit steen lassen hie
                                <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <app>
<note><q type="date">pfingsten schierst komende</q>26.05.1420</note>
</app> also, daz er in <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> czeite her czu uns
                        kume. So <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im hie in
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat vier tag ein sleht geleyte
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vor
                                <expan>allermen<ex>i</ex>kl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und ausserhalb der
                        stat für uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on
                            <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan> und wollen sein rede gern darümb
                        verhören; und wil er das also <expan>aufneme<ex>n</ex></expan>, so laszt uns
                        des ewr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider wissen, daz wir uns darnach wissen czu
                        richten. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
                        Valentini.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
